snippet.title: Bob the Builder: Festival of Fun - Nintendo DS Longplay [HD]
snippet.description:
Name: Bob the Builder: Festival of Fun

Description: Join Bob the Builder and the Team in an exciting new adventure! It's summer festival time in Sunflower Valley, with loads of music and food and fun for everyone. But before the festivities can begin there's work to be done! Can you help Bob and his friends get this party started?

Release Date: November 2008
